ouch with the real world and make meaningful connections with Oticon Real. This intelligent hearing aid helps you focus on speech by reducing disruptive sounds like sudden noise or wind."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"nyabhwkim","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"5o68mj3lz","text":"It is available in miniRITE and miniBTE styles, with rechargeable or traditional battery options."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"omp541tx5","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"clnqis8i1","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"3p3r7sxsi","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"okywhlm71","text":"Bluetooth® streaming for iPhone® and Android™"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"dvd0zq6ji","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"8uyjsxywv","text":"App control via Oticon Companion or ON app"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"0s12mgrb2","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"7a5dmmz0i","text":"Tinnitus SoundSupport™ for calming tinnitus relief"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"k15s5lpwn","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"j0aplc6qg","text":"Oticon Own"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"r7xe0vnfe","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"hu4wj9sc8","text":"Hearing loss is personal. Experience custom-fit hearing solutions with Oticon Own!"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"fbr1xcjuc","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"qn2xf5jwv","text":"This custom-molded, in-the-ear solution is designed to provide clear sound and effective listening even in noisy environments. It smartly distinguishes speech from background noise while staying virtually invisible."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"gygfgv4pe","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"mrc88q8ag","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"yohfu5i0t","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_typ