us SoundSupport™ system."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"z55lzjt6x","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"8wgvd0a9t","text":"This feature plays soothing background sounds such as white noise, soft ocean waves, or other custom tones that help reduce the perception of tinnitus. These sounds can be adjusted by an audiologist or hearing aid specialist to fit your personal comfort and listening needs."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"nswfn50na","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"peuqnvpex","text":"Oticon models that offer tinnitus relief include:"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"nuq2lfseh","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"7dtii7v6h","text":"Oticon Intent (premium)"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"8fcxix4m2","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"mngkde0wc","text":"Oticon Real"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"z1nfkkf49","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"3xqr39vgn","text":"Oticon More"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"1kebsj2rr","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"acbzqnwxy","text":"Oticon Own (custom in-the-ear styles)"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"ue57u75rg","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"corvl5jh8","text":"Oticon Zircon"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"5ljp65s2l","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"sx9ogqkzk","text":"Oticon Play PX (pediatric model)"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"8jp88fd70","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"si8fjdwrz","text":"Oticon Xceed (for severe to profound hearing loss)"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"y06tm9y2a","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"53t4qfawe","text":"Oticon Ruby"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"856c5kuf4","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"qmn3v2fp9","text":"Nearly all current Oticon models with the BrainHearing™ platform can be programmed for tinnitus management, making it easier to pair relief with your daily hearing correction."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"7ld69zmvk","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"3xyez4j2u","text":"If you’re experiencing tinnitus, our Lutz, FL audiologist and hearing aid specialist can recommend the best Oticon device to support your hearing and provide relief."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"3twu29dwt","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"ezlsth5co","text":"Find the Right Oticon Hearing Aid in Lutz, FL"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"pp2kukhpm","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"125qw20jg","text":"At JC Audiology, we can help you find the Oticon hearing aid that fits your hearing needs and lifestyle. As an authorized Oticon provider in Lutz, FL, we offer the latest models, expert fittings, and personalized care."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"yhz7cb5rt","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"70amvyx65","text":"Schedule your consultation today and take the next step toward clearer hearing and greater confidence."}]}]');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","brand_name","route","meta_title","meta_description","body_content") VALUES('hearing-aids__resound','hearing-aids__resound','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-21T06:06:26.429Z','2026-05-21T06:06:26.429Z','2026-05-21T06:06:26.429Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'ReSound Hearing Aids','/hearing-aids/resound/','ReSound Hearing Aids','JC Audiology is an authorized provider of ReSound hearing aids in Lutz, FL. Contact us to learn more!','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1043fae6","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-811bd68e","text":"JC Audiology is an authorized provider of ReSound hearing aids in Lutz, FL.","marks":["em","strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3ee1610a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9e550b58","text":"ReSound hearing aids are designed to help you hear more naturally and comfortably in all kinds of listening situations. Using advanced technology that works with the way the brain processes sound, ReSound hearing aids provide clear speech, balanced sound, and easy listening.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-935f0cea","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-08b4c2f8","text":"Many models offer Bluetooth streaming, rechargeable batteries, and smart app controls so you can adjust your settings anytime. With options for mild to severe hearing loss, ReSound makes it easier to stay connected, enjoy conversations, and fully engage in daily life.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9c4df60c","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3dd97cb5","text":"At JC Audiology, our audiologist and hearing aid specialist can help you choose the right ReSound hearing aid for your needs. We want you to hear for life, and we’ll make it possible through quality hearing aids and expert care!","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-c4641328","style":"h2","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8d8e251c","text":"ReSound Hearing Aids in Lutz, FL","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-d8988ec9","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2d67d7d2","text":"ReSound Enzo IA","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-b5c7dc91","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-c147ee65","text":"The ReSound Enzo IA is designed for severe to profound hearing loss. It is the world’s smallest rechargeable Super Power hearing aid and the first of its kind to support Bluetooth LE Audio and Auracast broadcast streaming.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0508efd9","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9680aec7","text":"With a stylish, durable design, the ReSound Enzo IA is built for the most challenging listening situations. It offers exceptional clarity, feedback control, and all-day battery life. ","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-88424e28","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-772e8814","text":"Unique Perks and Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-b0602fd2","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-94516da0","text":"Clear Focus: ","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-147dfb15","text":"Automatically reduces background noise while highlighting speech.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-587dfdd4","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-acc716f8","text":"360 All-Around listening: ","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7535a6c1","text":"Naturally shifts attention between voices and surrounding sounds.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-50fa03ed","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-01ec9a42","text":"Comfortable and weatherproof: ","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-880ca0cf","text":"Lightweight, all-day wear with protective nanocoating.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-010eb0b8","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-554bbbee","text":"Flexible connectivity: ","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-d1e19349","text":"Supports Bluetooth® LE Audio, Auracast™, and direct streaming from multiple devices.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0e853e0c","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-b4e36fff","text":"ReSound Vivia","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-31bfcee3","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-95770c0e","text":"The ReSound Vivia is designed to deliver clear, natural sound in a variety of listening environments. Built on ReSound’s latest platform, it uses advanced sound processing and artificial intelligence (AI) to intelligently adjust to your surroundings. Hear conversations in noisy places, enjoy music, or follow dialogue on TV with ease.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6683d0e3","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ee07ce54","text":"It also has All Access Directionality feature to help you focus on speech while still being aware of sounds around you. The Ultra Focus mode gives you an extra boost when listening to someone directly in front of you in challenging situations.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-f7897234","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7d2f0fd8","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-f2c6a750","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-28cd0ad2","text":"Long-lasting battery-even while streaming","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-44a95b92","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-a9949937","text":"Durable, weather-resistant design","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-abf61550","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-12758aa1","text":"Bluetooth and Auracast for smooth device and public audio connections","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-7d1856f8","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-6f2e37b0","text":"Auracast Assistant for hearing announcements in public venues","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0f844003","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2d2a8191","text":"ReSound Savi","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2894b86b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-772bcfb8","text":"ReSound Savi brings excellent sound quality, comfort, and the latest wireless features. The good news? It is offered at an accessible price point. It was just launched in February 2025, and it is one of ReSound’s most affordable hearing aids with advanced features.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-181a374b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-b944e1c6","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-56c4d668","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-e554054b","text":"All-day power for streaming and listening","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-a7f2bb45","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7967fa21","text":"Water and dust resistance","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-cc6fda58","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f1b40ee7","text":"Bluetooth® & Auracast™ for device and broadcast audio","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-955e