dex Allure offers the perfect blend of cutting-edge technology and elegant design. It is designed by experts to deliver the most natural hearing experience possible. Reconnect with the world and people around you through clear speech, accurate environmental sound processing, and highly-intuitive adjustments.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6f0b5b5b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1d5dfa95","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9b13f93f","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3293ca1e","text":"Powered by the W1 Chip","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-38c88e8b","text":": Widex’s fastest chip delivers quick, clear, and natural sound.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6eac3206","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-b5d6cfa2","text":"Allure PureSound™ with ZeroDelay Technology","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8ee6fc71","text":": Helps you hear speech without distortion or echo, creating a more lifelike experience.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-d39e2ed1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-c5d85cec","text":"Speech Enhancer Pro:","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-36eb2b54","text":" Lowers background noise so voices stand out, making conversations easier-even in noisy places.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2ef15b47","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2294a81c","text":"Dynamic Feedback Controller","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-b19fcc1d","text":": Adapts to your ear’s shape to reduce annoying whistling or squealing sounds.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-04bbb0d0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-098c053b","text":"Smooth Streaming","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ad59af3a","text":": Enjoy music, podcasts, and calls with steady sound-no sudden volume changes or outside interference.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9579df4a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-0e94f9b5","text":"Widex Allure App","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-58c253dc","text":": Easily adjust settings and personalize your hearing experience right from your smartphone.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4d6abeec","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-4a52ae1b","text":"Widex SmartRIC","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-23abc367","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3b9c09d7","text":"Widex SmartRIC hearing aids are designed for clear, natural sound. It comes with a slim, modern shape that’s comfortable to wear all day. It efficiently reduces wind and handling noise, making listening easier in quiet and noisy places.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1f54e229","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-fb3ed894","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2d2c2c3c","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-b709e439","text":"The Widex Moment app allows for easy personalization and fine-tuning of settings","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-74627c4b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-29a93b9f","text":"Bluetooth streaming works with both iPhone and Android devices","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3ad68f00","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-b5e65167","text":"Tinnitus relief is available through Widex Zen Therapy, offering a soothing soundscape","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"