aring aids are an ideal option if you want a personalized fit, modern features, and all-day listening comfort.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-dd0738fe","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-accca6ca","text":"Key Features:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-741ace0b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-97345c30","text":"Custom-fit design ensures a secure and personalized fit","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-38e1c1d1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3ead0b15","text":"Supports Bluetooth streaming and app-based adjustments","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-80ffcb35","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-798cb8ea","text":"Powered by size 10 or 312 disposable batteries with up to 150 hours of use","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-e874f549","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-94802dc7","text":"Offers built-in Zen Tinnitus Therapy for soothing soundscapes","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-42176371","style":"h2","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9baa815d","text":"Widex Assistive Listening Accessories","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-7f651e63","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-e2f69b58","text":"Take your hearing experience further with accessories designed to improve communication and convenience:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-c2eef5a3","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-0b6d4ee7","text":"Widex TV Play","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-c7bfddce","text":" streams high-quality audio directly from your television to your hearing aids","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9bb42c3c","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9db9028b","text":"Widex Sound Assist","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8212d12d","text":" functions as a microphone, remote control, and hands-free calling device","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-8b0eed86","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-900b882c","text":"Com-Dex, RC-Dex, and TV-Dex","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-d2b837f8","text":" provide additional ways to control your hearing aids and stay connected","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9c821038","style":"h2","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-fc275719","text":"Older Widex Models We Support","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4ac8f928","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-bd9f6f2d","text":"At JC Audiology, we continue to service and repair a range of older Widex hearing aids, including:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-46c53453","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f98ddda5","text":"Widex Evoke","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-125421e6","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-23514852","text":"Widex Beyond","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2f97f3c6","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-309c9bbf","text":"Widex Unique","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-74dce719","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8badee58","text":"Widex Dream","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-b7476e51","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ecdff16b","text":"If you have an older model, contact us to see how we can help maintain or repair your device.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2ee39c0b","style":"h2","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-418c2791","text":"Frequently Asked Questions – Widex Hearing Aids","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3376c9fe","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-175da69e","text":"How long do Widex hearing aids last?","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-7e5e591d","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-25e26fa2","text":"Widex hearing aids are made to be durable and usually last about three to five years. The exact lifespan depends on the model, how often you use them, and how well you care for them. Regular cleaning and check-ups with your hearing care provider can help them last longer. ","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9aab45c3","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1a26f4ad","text":"Do Widex hearing aids offer tinnitus relief?","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-d3e97e5a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-539d39b2","text":"Yes. Many Widex hearing aids include Zen Therapy, a built-in feature that plays gentle soundscapes and relaxation tones. These sounds can make tinnitus less noticeable and help you feel calmer during the day. Talk to our Lutz, FL audiologist to learn more.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0d7330b2","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-726b94c0","text":"Can I stream phone calls and music with Widex hearing aids?","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-ce562398","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9312bdbb","text":"Yes. Most newer Widex models have Bluetooth so you can stream phone calls, music, and other audio directly from compatible iPhone and Android devices. You can also use the Widex Moment app to adjust settings, switch programs, and control volume right from your phone. Talk to our Lutz, FL hearing aid specialist to learn more.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6cd21b38","style":"h2","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-21854665","text":"Find the Right Widex Hearing Aid in Lutz, FL","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-11a926a5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-db8cf596","text":"At JC Audiology, we’re more than happy to help you find the Widex hearing aid that’s right for your hearing needs, lifestyle, and budget. As an authorized Widex provider in Lutz, FL, we offer the latest models, personalized fittings, and long-term support.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-c03d2aad","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-fdbb17ff","text":"Contact us today to schedule a consultation and experience what Widex technology can do for your hearing!","marks":[]}]}]');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","brand_name","route","meta_title","meta_description","body_content") VALUES('hearing-aids__lyric','hearing-aids__lyric','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-26T00:00:00.000Z','2026-05-25T16:56:41.068Z','2026-05-26T00:00:00.000Z',NULL,NULL,12,'01KSG0ZE7F785WY03C7Z3AJ34B',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Lyric Hearing Aids','/hearing-aids/lyric/','Lyric Hearing Aids | JC Audiology','JC Audiology is an authorized Lyric hearing aid provider in Lutz, FL.','[{"_type":"block","_key":"h3uic30lt","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"8mmw9w2e3","text":"JC Audiology is an authorized Lyric hearing aid provider in Lutz, FL.","marks":["strong","em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"k26cg7bur","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"wlyzvz1ij","text":"Lyric hearing aids are known as the world’s first 100% invisible, extended-wear hearing solution. Lyric devices are placed deep inside your ear by a trained audiologist or hearing aid specialist, where they stay for weeks at a time. You can wear them all day and night without removing them, even while sleeping, showering, or exercising."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"266d0utqc","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"d2hgkuu76","text":"Because Lyric sits so close to your eardrum, it uses your ear’s natural shape to deliver clear, natural sound. Many people love Lyric because it’s out of sight, always ready, and works around the clock."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"oegycfrfj","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"yyvdwgulb","text":"Why Choose Lyric Hearing Aids?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"z5fs8kadf","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"bo2xd9tm4","text":"Completely invisible: No one will see that you''re wearing hearing aids."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"hjul7miyx","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"d3zhz5686","text":"24/7 hearing: Wear them while sleeping, talking on the phone, watching TV, or being outdoors."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"kdrbreqns","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"2t23c0yky","text":"Natural sound: Placed close to your eardrum for rich, clear sound."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"vffcmdr4s","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"0rzyn89km","text":"Low maintenance: No batteries to change or daily cleaning. Lyric is replaced every few months by our team."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"qwxq963jd","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"yk85y63l4","text":"Lyric hearing aids are especially helpful for people who want a no-fuss solution with great sound and total comfort."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"f4g8623op","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"kaqmorsvy","text":"How Lyric Works"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"ecr8wa7o5","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"5hhqegqd6","text":"Lyric hearing aids are placed in your ear canal by our audiologist or hearing aid specialist using a safe, comfortable procedure in our office. Once in place, they stay there for up to 2-3 months. When the battery runs out, you simply come back to JC Audiology, and we replace the device with a fresh one."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"5zct2erhw","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"xvutcd2ke","text":"You can still use headphones, talk on the phone, or wear helmets without any interference. Lyric is designed to handle daily activities, including showering (but not swimming or diving)."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"yaetz971l","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"3hhalblxq","text":"Benefits of Lyric Hearing Aids"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"dp5h4n9to","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"pjaqjbevx","text":"Always on: You don''t have to put them in or take them out each day."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"nz04ffe38","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"b5v53fj9o","text":"No daily handling: Great for people who have trouble with small hearing aid parts."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"mc7a1t12n","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"nt4fo5jmy","text":"Better for active lifestyles: You can work out, hike, or play sports without worrying about them falling out."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"pf5hc2xmf","style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1,"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"hfrzqewee","text":"Clearer, more natural sound: The deep placement in your ear helps process sound like normal hearing."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"7xhe2dtfn","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"2w389s5rp","text":"Are Lyric Hearing Aids Right for You?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"5kw4hvp1x","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"4z7oyn07v","text":"Lyric isn’t right for everyone. Your ear shape, ear health, and hearing needs will help determine if Lyric is a good choice. Our Lutz, FL audiologist or hearing aid specialist will do a hearing test and ear exam to see if Lyric will work for you."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"0lb4ltpwz","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"h2yxeghet","text":"If Lyric is not the best option, we can recommend other hearing aids that still meet your comfort and sound needs."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"uz0725s20","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"01ld149js","text":"JC Audiology provides a wide selection of hearing aids in Lutz, FL."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"vhoqjayoy","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"rjw8909n4","text":"FAQs About Lyric Hearing Aids"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"evj1bikg0","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"u4g10odz7","text":"Can I remove Lyric myself?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"uasxbexg0","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"jx6uceutt","text":"Lyric is meant to be placed and removed by a trained provider. You’ll come to JC Audiology for replacements."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"3lfxvry5n","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"34ps5fch2","text":"Can I shower or sleep with Lyric?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"x3yvvh1cf","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"7p7pk5jcr","text":"Yes! Lyric can be worn 24/7, including in the shower and while sleeping. Just avoid swimming or putting your head fully underwater."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"bwedmtim1","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"lhyc4w8ta","text":"How long does each Lyric device last?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"y3ksfhjkx","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"juf5uouwj","text":"Most last about 2?3 months. When the battery runs out, we replace it during a quick visit to our office."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"ujhdtjqcn","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"67exe32ec","text":"Is Lyric comfortable to wear?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"tguo2ong1","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"pskrq0msg","text":"Yes, most people forget they’re even wearing them after a short adjustment period."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"84b9fq9dv","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"9m7a1j005","text":"Will Lyric work for all types of hearing loss?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"gbiksx058","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"8ycq1ciz1","text":"Lyric is best for mild to moderate hearing loss. We’ll do a hearing test to see if it’s a good fit for you."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"1q7p86kmn","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"tcwxfzvsq","text":"Try Lyric Hearing Aids at JC Audiology"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"d2sp654xp","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"dj6tbe2r7","text":"If you want hearing aids that are invisible, easy to wear, and always ready, Lyric may be the perfect solution. At JC Audiology, our audiologist and hearing aid specialist are trained and certified to fit Lyric hearing aids in Lutz, FL. Call us today to schedule your Lyric hearing aid consultation and start hearing for life!"}]}]');
INSERT INTO "ec_homepage" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","hero_intro","hero_content","appointment_cta_url","intro_section_intro","intro_h1_title","intro_body_content","badge_1","badge_2","badge_3","badge_4","testimonial_eyebrow_text","testimonial_h2_title","testimonial_body_content","faq_h2_title","faq_body_content","faq_cta_url","faq_items") VALUES('home','home','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-21T09:52:13.636Z','2026-05-21T15:44:30.433Z','2026-05-21T09:52:13.636Z',NULL,NULL,25,'01KS50EEVYQEA5PQKEHWGR6JKB',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Hearing For Life','Let''s help you make meaningful connections with expert hearing care!','https://jc-audiology-staging.local-981.workers.dev/schedule-appointment/','JC Audiology','LUTZ, FL AUDIOLOGIST, HEARING AID SPECIALIST & HEARING AIDS','[{"_type":"block","_key":"g3fjl4kl1","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"uyuggmumo","text":"At JC Audiology, we understand how hearing loss can creep up on you and affect your daily life in subtle, frustrating ways. Hearing loss can feel isolating, and over time, it can even affect your mental sharpness. The good news is that treating your hearing loss can help."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"pn35txozs","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"u0nnz6ohs","text":"Let us help you regain the joy of hearing and the quality of life you deserve."}]}]','{"id":"media-homepage-badge-american-academy-of-audiology","provider":"local","filename":"cf0c55f6-american-academy-of-audiology.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":340,"height":240,"alt":"American Academy of Audiology logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage/cf0c55f6-american-academy-of-audiology.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-badge-academy-of-doctors-of-audiology","provider":"local","filename":"a717e552-academy-of-doctors-of-audiology.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":340,"height":240,"alt":"Academy of Doctors of Audiology logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage/a717e552-academy-of-doctors-of-audiology.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-badge-asha","provider":"local","filename":"81b6f248-asha.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":340,"height":240,"alt":"ASHA logo with face profiles and soundwave icon","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage/81b6f248-asha.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-badge-ihs","provider":"local","filename":"90fe12a0-ihs.png","mimeType":"image/png","width":340,"height":240,"alt":"IHS logo with heartbeat line through letters","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage/90fe12a0-ihs.png","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','What Our Patients Are Saying','Client Testimonials','[{"_type":"block","_key":"iiyol1o9u","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"dxyxj7piv","text":"Your hearing health is our top priority, and we are dedicated to providing compassionate care. Hear from our patients in Lutz, FL, about their experiences with our services!"}]}]','Frequently Asked Questions','[{"_type":"block","_key":"nws01pl63","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"q4mhg2e0c","text":"Can''t find the answers you''re looking for?\n"},{"_type":"span","_key":"ivm1oiusa","text":"Reach out us."}]}]','https://jc-audiology-staging.local-981.workers.dev/contact/','[{"question":"How do I know if I need a hearing aid?","answer":"If you''re experiencing difficulty hearing in conversations, particularly in noisy environments, frequently turning up the volume on the TV or radio, or feeling isolated from social interactions, it may be time to consider a hearing test. An audiologist can evaluate your hearing and help determine if a hearing aid is necessary."},{"question":"What is the difference between hearing aids and personal sound amplification products (PSAPs)?","answer":"Hearing aids are FDA-approved devices specifically designed for people with hearing loss. They are customizable, programmed by an audiologist, and regulated for medical use. PSAPs, on the other hand, are general amplifiers intended for individuals without hearing loss and do not offer the same level of customization or professional support."},{"question":"Can I get a hearing aid without a hearing test?","answer":"Yes, you can purchase over-the-counter (OTC) hearing aids without a hearing test. However, these devices are typically intended for adults with mild to moderate hearing loss. A hearing test with an audiologist ensures that you get a personalized solution that addresses your specific needs, including identifying any underlying medical conditions."},{"question":"How can hearing aids help with tinnitus?","answer":"Hearing aids can help mask the ringing or buzzing associated with tinnitus by amplifying external sounds, making the internal noise less noticeable. Some hearing aids are specifically designed to include features that provide sound therapy to help alleviate tinnitus symptoms."}]');
INSERT INTO "ec_homepage_hearing_solutions_section" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","section_title","section_subheading","featured_image","brands_label","brand_logo_1","brand_logo_2","brand_logo_3","brand_logo_4","brand_logo_5","brand_logo_6","brand_logo_7","brand_logo_8","services") VALUES('our-hearing-solutions','our-hearing-solutions','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-21T06:57:16.611Z','2026-05-21T07:40:40.652Z','2026-05-21T06:57:16.611Z',NULL,NULL,15,'01KS4QK8DWWPCG1WQJ0A4SNVQX',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Our Hearing Aids & Protection Solutions in Lutz, FL','Our Hearing Solutions','{"id":"media-homepage-5b25cc48-jcaudiology-hearing-aids-featured","provider":"local","filename":"5b25cc48-jcaudiology-hearing-aids-featured.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":1024,"height":683,"alt":"Two hearing aids in charging case beside color sample set on lanyard","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/5b25cc48-jcaudiology-hearing-aids-featured.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','Supported Hearing Aid Brands','{"id":"media-homepage-d7737348-phonak-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"d7737348-phonak-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"phonak-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/d7737348-phonak-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-e4d08723-oticon-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"e4d08723-oticon-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"oticon-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/e4d08723-oticon-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-8ee33448-widex-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"8ee33448-widex-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"widex-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/8ee33448-widex-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-2572bb02-starkey-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"2572bb02-starkey-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"starkey-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/2572bb02-starkey-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-c826ce45-resound-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"c826ce45-resound-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"resound-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/c826ce45-resound-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-76fb611a-signia-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"76fb611a-signia-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"signia-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/76fb611a-signia-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-62cc30e4-unitron-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"62cc30e4-unitron-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"unitron-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/62cc30e4-unitron-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','{"id":"media-homepage-6846f282-lyric-logo-300x300","provider":"local","filename":"6846f282-lyric-logo-300x300.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":300,"height":300,"alt":"lyric-logo","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/6846f282-lyric-logo-300x300.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','[{"service_title":"Hearing Aids","description":"We offer a wide selection of high-quality, hearing aids from trusted manufacturers like Phonak, Oticon, ReSound, Unitron, Widex, Starkey, Signia, and Lyric. Our expert team will help you choose the best hearing aid for your unique needs and lifestyle.","service_url":"/hearing-aids-products/"},{"service_title":"Hearing Aid Batteries and Accessories","description":"To keep your hearing aids performing their best, we provide a variety of essential accessories, including batteries, cleaning tools, and more. Count on us to make maintaining your hearing aids simple, ensuring their longevity and superior performance.","service_url":"/hearing-aids-products/hearing-aid-batteries/"},{"service_title":"Assistive Listening Devices","description":"If you struggle to hear clearly in noisy places or during phone calls, our assistive listening devices can help. These tools are designed to enhance your hearing in challenging environments. Whether you’re at home, at work, or on the go, you can enjoy clearer conversations with ALDs.","service_url":"/hearing-aids-products/hearing-aid-alternatives/"},{"service_title":"Custom Ear Protection","description":"Whether you’re a musician, a swimmer, or an employee constantly exposed to a noisy environment, our custom-fit earplugs offer the best protection you need. We provide custom ear protection tailored to fit your ears perfectly!","service_url":"/custom-hearing-protection/"}]');
INSERT INTO "ec_homepage_services_section" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","section_title","section_subheading","featured_image","services") VALUES('our-services','our-services','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-21T06:57:16.610Z','2026-05-21T11:36:50.027Z','2026-05-21T06:57:16.610Z',NULL,NULL,17,'01KS4QBTKMVVK3NBQ1X0567ZB9',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Audiology Services in Lutz, FL','Our Services','{"id":"media-homepage-bcc71369-jc-audiology-services-01","provider":"local","filename":"bcc71369-jc-audiology-services-01.webp","mimeType":"image/webp","width":1200,"height":800,"alt":"Clinician uses otoscope to examine woman’s ear in exam room","meta":{"storageKey":"homepage-sections/bcc71369-jc-audiology-services-01.webp","caption":null,"blurhash":null,"dominantColor":null}}','[{"service_title":"Hearing Evaluations","description":"JC Audiology offers comprehensive hearing assessments to accurately diagnose your hearing health. These tests help identify the degree and type of hearing loss you may have. Trust us to provide tailored solutions to match your unique hearing needs.","service_url":"/audiology-services/hearing-tests/"},{"service_title":"Tinnitus Evaluation and Support","description":"If you experience ringing, buzzing, or other “phantom sounds” in your ears, we can help. Our tinnitus evaluations help identify the root causes of your symptoms. We provide personalized treatment plans designed to ease the discomfort and help you regain peace and clarity.","service_url":"/audiology-services/tinnitus-evaluation-support/"},{"service_title":"Hearing Aid Services","description":"From helping you select the right hearing aid to expert fitting, cleaning, and repairs, we support you throughout your hearing aid journey. Our goal is to ensure that you have the best hearing experience possible, no matter where you are.","service_url":"/audiology-services/hearing-aid-services/"},{"service_title":"Hearing Aid Fittings","description":"A proper hearing aid fitting is essential to achieving the best results. At JC Audiology, we focus on fitting each device precisely to your unique needs, ensuring maximum comfort and performance for enhanced hearing and quality of life.","service_url":"/audiology-services/hearing-aid-fittings/"},{"service_title":"Hearing Aid Cleaning and Repair","description":"If your hearing aid isn’t performing at its best, we’re here to help. Our quick and reliable cleaning and repair services will restore your device’s functionality. Enjoy clear and comfortable hearing with JC Audiology.","service_url":"/audiology-services/sensorineural-hearing-loss/"}]');
INSERT INTO "ec_schedule_appointment_page" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","page_title","route","meta_title","meta_description","scheduler_embed") VALUES('schedule-appointment','schedule-appointment','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-21T11:21:21.288Z','2026-05-21T11:21:21.288Z','2026-05-21T11:21:21.288Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Schedule Appointment','/schedule-appointment/','Schedule Appointment','Schedule your hearing evaluation or consultation with JC Audiology. Get personalized care from expert audiologists and book your appointment today.','<iframe id="ceschedule" src="https://www.hearinghealthportal.com/scheduling/schedule.aspx?key=103472-9083&amp;embed=true" width="100%" height="600px" frameborder="0" style="border: 0;"></iframe>');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-01-01','audiology-services-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I test my own hearing?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-01','Can I test my own hearing?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4o75kx6b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-aq4d8q5u","text":"You ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-bube64qu","text":"can","marks":["em"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-xb8rcxei","text":" test your own hearing through online hearing tests and apps that offer basic screening. However, these tests don''t replace the accuracy of a professional hearing test. Getting a professional hearing test from an audiologist is still the best option.","marks":[]}]}]','93f3929',1,'65b65e0');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-01-02','audiology-services-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Are online hearing tests any good?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-01','Are online hearing tests any good?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-yvyhbd2d","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-vtx9gsv9","text":"Again, online hearing tests can give you a general idea of how well you hear, but they cannot replace a full evaluation by an audiologist.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-t1bevlux","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qk0pyzg5","text":"Online hearing tests just check if you can hear tones through headphones or speakers. They can''t identify the exact type or cause of hearing loss, assess how clearly you understand speech, and detect underlying medical conditions that may be affecting your hearing.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hm6qujt5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ievgj20l","text":"At JC Audiology, we offer accurate, comprehensive testing to help you hear your best.","marks":[]}]}]','3080a78',2,'a39331e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-02-01','audiology-services-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Should I go to an audiologist for tinnitus?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-02','Should I go to an audiologist for tinnitus?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-v673v8xs","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-pj6211qa","text":"Yes! An audiologist is trained to evaluate and treat tinnitus. If you''re hearing phantom sounds or the typical \"ringing in the ears\", an audiologist at JC Audiology can perform a thorough examination to identify potential triggers and determine whether your tinnitus is connected to hearing loss.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4qtikci1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-momnnbfe","text":"Based on the results, we may recommend helpful tools like sound therapy, hearing aids with built-in masking features, or relaxation techniques to address tinnitus symptoms. We''ll also teach you how to manage the daily effects of tinnitus on your focus, sleep, and emotional well-being. ","marks":[]}]}]','5b1a192',1,'4b926c0');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-02-02','audiology-services-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Is tinnitus a brain problem?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-02','Is tinnitus a brain problem?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4tcw0pth","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-337o2v8q","text":"While tinnitus often begins with the ears, it also involves the brain''s auditory system. When hearing loss or damage limits the sound input to the brain, the brain may compensate by creating its own sound. This is where tinnitus enters the scene.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-im0v66sq","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9dbnyucq","text":"Many treatments for tinnitus are programmed to reduce the brain''s perception of that sound. Approaches like sound therapy, hearing aids, or cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT) help retrain your brain and reduce how noticeable the ringing or buzzing becomes.","marks":[]}]}]','bbd4035',2,'25e8b3a');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-02-03','audiology-services-accordion-02-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'What happens if tinnitus is not treated?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-02','What happens if tinnitus is not treated?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-wj1fveq9","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-rraqi70s","text":"Over time, untreated tinnitus may increase stress, anxiety, or frustration. Many people with tinnitus struggle to fall asleep or stay focused during the day.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3mp8pep8","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-q2oz8iy9","text":"If tinnitus is linked to untreated hearing loss, ignoring it can also lead to worsening hearing problems. By addressing tinnitus early, you can improve your comfort and prevent tinnitus from interfering with daily activities. Let our Lutz, FL audiologists guide you toward tinnitus relief!","marks":[]}]}]','1f452c9',3,'4682479');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-03-01','audiology-services-accordion-03-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.348Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How long does it take to get fitted for a hearing aid?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-03','How long does it take to get fitted for a hearing aid?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-pcjc7k4w","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-0sqz0hw9","text":"The hearing aid fitting process typically takes about one to two hours. After completing a thorough hearing evaluation, our audiologist will discuss your results and recommend hearing aids that best fit your hearing needs, lifestyle, and preferences.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6ioe2cun","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qmoh50kk","text":"Once a hearing aid is chosen, an audiologist will program it with precise measurements (including real-ear measurements) to ensure optimal sound quality and performance.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hk4me03i","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-mz1ky8zy","text":"We will also show you how to properly insert, remove, and care for your new device, answering any questions you may have.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0kpwi1jg","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f5i144xm","text":"While the hearing aid fitting is usually completed in a single visit, follow-up appointments are expected. These follow-up appointments ensure comfort and are aimed to assist you in adjusting to amplified sounds over time.","marks":[]}]}]','68ffd89',1,'7c64daa');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-03-02','audiology-services-accordion-03-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How does an audiologist fit a hearing aid?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-03','How does an audiologist fit a hearing aid?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-x3q8blxp","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-dbh1p5go","text":"The process of hearing aid fitting begins after a complete hearing evaluation. Based on the hearing test result, an audiologist will select the most appropriate hearing aid model and program it to meet your hearing profile.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-se6m5kyv","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-4up82zrz","text":"During the fitting session, an audiologist will perform real-ear measurements to ensure the hearing aid provides the correct amplification for your ear canal''s acoustics. The audiologist will also adjust the physical fit of the device.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-jaqxxj6t","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qo1ozumk","text":"When the right (and most comfortable) fit is achieved, you''ll be taught how to insert and remove the hearing aid, clean and maintain it. This will also be the perfect time to discuss any related apps or accessories.","marks":[]}]}]','ab8abf7',2,'4971733');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-03-03','audiology-services-accordion-03-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can you get a hearing aid without a test?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-03','Can you get a hearing aid without a test?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-b07xadtu","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-csvwdl6k","text":"Yes, you can purchase over-the-counter (OTC) hearing aids without a hearing test. However, OTC hearing aids don''t offer the same personalized fitting or professional support as prescription hearing aids provided by an audiologist.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-8id0iz9a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-zruhnzeo","text":"By having a professional hearing evaluation at JC Audiology, you''ll receive expert advice, a customized solution, and the ability to identify any underlying medical conditions that could affect your hearing.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-8t4z0ni1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8zwjggmn","text":"If you''re uncertain about your hearing, starting with a comprehensive diagnostic test is the best way to ensure you get the right care.","marks":[]}]}]','cc0b9d9',3,'b90124e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-04-01','audiology-services-accordion-04-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'What are the common problems that require hearing aid repair?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-04','What are the common problems that require hearing aid repair?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-lx60jf6z","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-5jx2mzpm","text":"Some common issues that may need repair include:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-72lcm3bk","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-zvba02np","text":"No sound or low volume","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-eyiysxhw","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9usc4064","text":"Distorted or fuzzy sound","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-eu0cmf9d","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-82hqfrdb","text":"Feedback or whistling","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-wiqyngqb","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-4vncu965","text":"Visible damage","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1}]','68215d5',1,'014aec3');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-04-02','audiology-services-accordion-04-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How long does it take to repair a hearing aid?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-04','How long does it take to repair a hearing aid?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-08jgzeg0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-lfqbc10m","text":"The turnaround time for hearing aid repair depends on the issue. Minor fixes, such as replacing wax guards or cleaning tubing, can be completed in-house within a few minutes.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-7sp7r4tp","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1p3e0q1d","text":"However, if your device has bigger issues that need manufacturer service, repairs might take several days to two weeks. ","marks":[]}]}]','b1bb045',2,'c96c4db');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-04-03','audiology-services-accordion-04-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I fix my hearing aid at home?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-04','Can I fix my hearing aid at home?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-8edgi6j0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-lngoovgk","text":"Technically, yes, you can fix some minor hearing aid issues at home. However, more complex device issues should be handled by a professional.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-kmzbl3sm","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-33go9pkl","text":"If your hearing aid isn''t working properly, you can run basic troubleshooting. Most manufacturers also provide troubleshooting guides in their user manuals or apps.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-57oplgfe","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-j7jl24qb","text":"If your hearing device still isn''t working even after troubleshooting, it would be best to contact your audiologist or hearing aid provider.","marks":[]}]}]','c852914',3,'14135fb');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-05-01','audiology-services-accordion-05-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Why should I use hearing protection?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-05','Why should I use hearing protection?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-s03v7niv","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-k3n8l4si","text":"Exposure to loud sounds can permanently damage your hearing. Wearing proper protection reduces your risk of damage and helps you maintain your hearing health for the long run.","marks":[]}]}]','d8caf6e',1,'c647c1b');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-05-02','audiology-services-accordion-05-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Are custom earplugs better than store-bought ones?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-05','Are custom earplugs better than store-bought ones?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6orxhdm1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9k4u1eai","text":"Yes. Custom earplugs are made to fit the unique ear shape so they provide a more secure and comfortable fit compared to generic options. The snug fit also helps block out noise or water more effectively.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-d38m2o44","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-75t5isap","text":"Another benefit of custom earplugs is the opportunity for customization. If you want reliable performance, comfort, and long-term value, custom earplugs are worth the investment.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-8bkikdkb","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-131vkcdj","text":"Our Lutz, FL audiologist and hearing aid specialist can help you choose the right type and ensure the perfect fit.","marks":[]}]}]','9815a30',2,'f7e21b5');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services-accordion-05-03','audiology-services-accordion-05-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I still hear people talking with earplugs in?','audiology-services','audiology-services-accordion-05','Can I still hear people talking with earplugs in?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-kl2uazmf","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-lbtfoaab","text":"Yes, many custom earplugs are smartly designed to reduce loud background noise while still letting speech remain clear. They''re a great choice for musicians or anyone who needs to protect their hearing without losing the ability to communicate.","marks":[]}]}]','fddf672',3,'223f7e5');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-01-01','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Why Real Ear Measurement Matters','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-01','Why Real Ear Measurement Matters','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6hgqayna","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-slc8lq4w","text":"Everyone’s ears are different. REM makes sure your hearing aids match your ear’s unique shape and hearing needs. This means clearer speech, better comfort, and happier hearing.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-ntbw3ltg","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2sjrkg69","text":"At JC Audiology, we always include REM as part of your fitting to help you get the most from your hearing aids.","marks":[]}]}]','cc6f783',1,'f9a4235');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-02-01','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Why Follow-Up Visits Are Important','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-02','Why Follow-Up Visits Are Important','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-v5o3m8ux","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7inm4abt","text":"After your first fitting, follow-up visits help us make changes based on your experience. We adjust your hearing aids to make sure they fit well and sound great in your daily life.","marks":[]}]}]','4abda61',1,'0bbf5e1');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03-01','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Are hearing aid fittings covered by insurance?','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03','Are hearing aid fittings covered by insurance?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-8gn7v8d5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-x6zkphgt","text":"It depends on your plan. Medicare usually does not cover hearing aids, but some private insurance or veterans’ benefits might. Check with your provider for details.","marks":[]}]}]','d421bb1',1,'7628981');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03-02','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How can I make my hearing aids more comfortable?','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03','How can I make my hearing aids more comfortable?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-z5ghr69k","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8edgdekl","text":"If your hearing aids feel uncomfortable, tell your audiologist. We can adjust the fit, try different ear tips, or make custom molds to help.","marks":[]}]}]','f04f132',2,'2ee6e84');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03-03','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How long does a hearing aid fitting take?','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings','audiology-services__hearing-aid-fittings-accordion-03','How long does a hearing aid fitting take?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-w0vce2d5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2m42qbjn","text":"The first fitting usually takes about an hour. You’ll likely need a few follow-up visits to fine-tune the fit and settings.","marks":[]}]}]','087c8bb',3,'47ed7e5');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-services-accordion-01-01','audiology-services__hearing-aid-services-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Education & Support','audiology-services__hearing-aid-services','audiology-services__hearing-aid-services-accordion-01','Education & Support','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-zf04qjf0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8843t8a2","text":"Done with hearing aid fitting? Our care for you doesn’t end there! We’re here to make sure you succeed with your hearing aids.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0na0i6nq","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-lvndllii","text":"We’ll teach you how to insert and remove your devices, how to change or charge your batteries, and how to clean your hearing aids properly. We’ll also share with you communication strategies so you can enjoy and be fully confident with your new hearing aids.","marks":[]}]}]','8c7e40c',1,'321d049');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-aid-services-accordion-01-02','audiology-services__hearing-aid-services-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Real Ear Measurements','audiology-services__hearing-aid-services','audiology-services__hearing-aid-services-accordion-01','Real Ear Measurements','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1l0j4w43","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-yhpcim9u","text":"Each ear is unique and has its own shape. Real Ear Measurements (REM) ensure your hearing aids deliver the best possible sound for your unique ear. A small microphone is placed in your ear canal to ensure the devices are amplifying sound properly for your ear’s individual acoustics.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-oyaienfw","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-133fxx8e","text":"It’s all about making sure your hearing aids are just right.","marks":[]}]}]','e3236ab',2,'b5de92c');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01-01','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Hearing Tests We Offer at JC Audiology','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01','Hearing Tests We Offer at JC Audiology','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-sc8psi0v","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f761rysf","text":"We provide a full range of hearing tests to get a clear picture of your hearing health. Some of our commonly performed hearing tests include:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6byb28vl","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-oej16cy9","text":"Pure-Tone Audiometry","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-athc4seo","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-gdvw1kf7","text":"Speech Audiometry","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1v6ieidr","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9amsmzj6","text":"Tympanometry","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1}]','c850654',1,'6355409');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01-02','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'What to Expect During Your Hearing Test','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01','What to Expect During Your Hearing Test','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hwglgtgc","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-97bdpe15","text":"Our comprehensive hearing tests in Tampa include a quick, non-invasive exam and a full set of listening checks that usually take 30–45 minutes.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-cb6m7go7","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-v90w97kq","text":"We’ll start by reviewing your medical history, your hearing concerns, and the situations where you notice trouble, so we have a clear baseline for your overall hearing health.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0eb8sssn","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-6s0am9qz","text":"Next, we’ll examine your ears for issues like earwax buildup or signs of infection.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1546sx2a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-j5ia0olu","text":"During the test itself, you’ll listen through headphones to tones and speech at different pitches and volumes, and you’ll respond each time you hear them. Afterward, we’ll explain your results and review the next steps, if any are needed.","marks":[]}]}]','8a78981',2,'05ceb57');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01-03','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Your Hearing Test Results','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-01','Your Hearing Test Results','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-nkyn63ka","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-q7wodrg9","text":"After testing, an audiologist or hearing aid specialist will explain your results using an audiogram.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-jw30ww55","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-bzej92q6","text":"If hearing loss is detected, we’ll discuss treatment options. These may include hearing aids, sound therapy, cochlear implants, assistive listening devices, or medical referrals.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-iwne4eh7","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ysbplgry","text":"At JC Audiology, our goal is to help you hear more clearly and enjoy better communication every day.","marks":[]}]}]','f14a08f',3,'73f0bfa');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-01','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I test my own hearing?','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02','Can I test my own hearing?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4kz7sd7b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-txpmwre9","text":"Online screenings are available but can’t replace the accuracy of a professional hearing test.","marks":[]}]}]','1ab7206',1,'f45927f');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-02','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Are hearing tests safe?','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02','Are hearing tests safe?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4fzr59mz","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-cj0d6u12","text":"Yes! They’re completely safe, painless, and non-invasive.","marks":[]}]}]','44275d5',2,'17654f4');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-03','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Are online hearing tests reliable?','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02','Are online hearing tests reliable?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-27u8spmt","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ej8cul80","text":"Online hearing tests or apps may provide a general idea of your hearing. But there’s a catch – these online tests lack the detailed accuracy of an audiologist’s evaluation.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4edfopis","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-vltnhugp","text":"All testing at JC Audiology is done in a state of the art sound treated room that is calibrated and continually certified, and provides the most optimal hearing test accuracy possible.","marks":[]}]}]','b5bb7dc',3,'77c597a');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-04','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-04','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I take a hearing test on my phone?','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02','Can I take a hearing test on my phone?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-5yspdp8y","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-pt5smxvc","text":"Some apps offer basic screenings, but they cannot diagnose hearing loss or its causes like a professional can.","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-mh3ci7cc","text":"All testing at JC Audiology is done in a state of the art sound treated room that is calibrated and continually certified, and provides the most optimal hearing test accuracy possible.","marks":[]}]}]','ad36082',4,'2b15c94');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-05','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02-05','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How often should I get a hearing test?','audiology-services__hearing-tests','audiology-services__hearing-tests-accordion-02','How often should I get a hearing test?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-z8ufhl5z","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-802nlgg6","text":"If your hearing is normal, every 3 to 5 years is enough. If you have hearing loss, use hearing aids, or face frequent noise exposure, yearly testing is recommended.","marks":[]}]}]','1bad79c',5,'45cab7e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__real-ear-measurement-accordion-01-01','audiology-services__real-ear-measurement-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.349Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How Does Real Ear Measurement Work?','audiology-services__real-ear-measurement','audiology-services__real-ear-measurement-accordion-01','How Does Real Ear Measurement Work?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6ujnecv5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-bl03zyqf","text":"The process is simple and comfortable. First, the audiologist or hearing aid specialist will gently place a very thin probe microphone in your ear canal. This is done while you are wearing your hearing aid. The microphone sits close to your eardrum but does not touch it, so you should not feel any pain.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-jrgie6dm","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-k9exe94z","text":"Next, a speaker nearby plays different test sounds. The microphone measures how these sounds behave inside your ear canal. This gives us a real ear response, which is like a fingerprint of your ear’s unique acoustics.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-m8iugx68","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-k3m7n95c","text":"We then compare these measurements to your ideal hearing levels, based on your hearing test results. If your hearing aids are not delivering the right amount of amplification, we make changes on the spot. You can hear the difference instantly.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hgrobv93","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-thxxmeqj","text":"Once everything sounds balanced, we verify the results one last time to ensure accuracy.","marks":[]}]}]','417a99b',1,'d24d146');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-01-01','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Signs You Might Have Sensorineural Hearing Loss','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-01','Signs You Might Have Sensorineural Hearing Loss','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-46lf8voo","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-kxyd7po0","text":"SNHL can happen slowly over time or all at once. Some common signs include:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-ychs8fjz","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-zomth60d","text":"Trouble hearing soft voices or whispers","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-vlvmw25m","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-20kvhxg1","text":"Feeling like people are mumbling","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-m9t04hnz","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-zolzkf0p","text":"Often asking others to repeat themselves","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-r3jabj6p","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-m034tdjo","text":"Difficulty understanding speech in noisy places","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-znv5524e","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ckfhj8mz","text":"Hearing ringing, buzzing, or hissing sounds (tinnitus)","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-6dokig8q","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7iz6t4en","text":"Hearing better in one ear than the other","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-o3vtewqz","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-if6qbiac","text":"Sounds seem far away or unclear","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-51okdaqr","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-gn2gjssy","text":"Difficulty hearing high-pitched sounds like birds or children’s voices","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-jqheb8of","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-658514bg","text":"If you notice any of these signs, it’s time to schedule a hearing check with an audiologist or hearing aid specialist at JC Audiology.","marks":[]}]}]','43fac04',1,'9ab3e02');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02-01','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Hearing Solutions For SNHL','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02','Hearing Solutions For SNHL','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-art8q4i5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-grv91b29","text":"Hearing Aids","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-0mu4mbh4","text":" – Great for mild to moderate SNHL. Today’s devices can have features like Bluetooth streaming, rechargeable batteries, and special microphones that make it easier to hear in noisy places.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3wjjetiv","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-g7i0d5ff","text":"Cochlear Implants","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-jalfupg7","text":" – Used for severe hearing loss when hearing aids are no longer enough. These devices send sound signals directly to the hearing nerve.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hutps2k1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-jutb377s","text":"Bone-Anchored Hearing Aids (BAHA)","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9mixah07","text":" – Helpful for some people with hearing loss in one ear or mixed hearing loss. They send sound through the bone instead of the ear canal.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-nnxirmdt","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-w20csi8q","text":"Our audiologists and hearing aid specialists will help you choose the option that gives you the clearest sound and most comfort.","marks":[]}]}]','7c8eeae',1,'6fce07f');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02-02','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can SNHL Be Cured?','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02','Can SNHL Be Cured?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9ep511fr","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-bm39jyxf","text":"Right now, there is no cure for SNHL because the damaged hair cells in the ear do not grow back. But with early treatment (using hearing aids, cochlear implants, or other devices), you can greatly improve your ability to hear and stay active in conversations.","marks":[]}]}]','e407abe',2,'f8d7a4e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02-03','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How to Protect Your Hearing','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss','audiology-services__sensorineural-hearing-loss-accordion-02','How to Protect Your Hearing','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-t08nfkl8","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-mzwn45j3","text":"While not all SNHL can be prevented, you can lower your risk by:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-woaltfr7","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-vcd1wdvw","text":"Wearing hearing protection","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-t0kxva2y","text":" – Use earplugs or earmuffs at concerts, when using loud tools, or around loud machinery.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-v9ccx7re","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qb0rerxv","text":"Keeping volume safe","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-in5f0asl","text":" – Follow the 60/60 rule: listen at no more than 60% volume for no more than 60 minutes at a time.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-c7m4lxhz","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-x7j4vvg4","text":"Taking breaks","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-pjzd2j7j","text":" – Give your ears time to rest from headphones or earbuds.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-q4vutztp","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-jnbesc7p","text":"Being aware of medications","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-moqqcp9c","text":" – Ask your doctor if your medicine could affect your hearing.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-kffq8960","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-e0cdb54o","text":"Getting regular hearing check-ups","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-x2l8yhsd","text":" – Early testing can find problems before they get worse.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1}]','1d63200',3,'c81b705');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-01','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Sound Therapy','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01','Sound Therapy','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-06v4g0fa","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9l1utsby","text":"Sound therapy involves gentle background sounds to help your brain tune out the ringing. Think of white noise machines that create a steady, calming hum.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-cag1rta9","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-h2kyzzn1","text":"Nature sounds like wind blowing, ocean waves or rainfall work great, too. Even better, many modern hearing aids come with built-in sound masking features that quietly soothe your tinnitus throughout the day.","marks":[]}]}]','5396838',1,'07bf9f9');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-02','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Hearing Aids','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01','Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-f13rr5sw","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7jbct73f","text":"If your tinnitus tags along with hearing loss, hearing aids can be a real game-changer. They make everyday sounds louder and clearer, helping your brain focus on real noise instead of the ringing. Plus, lots of hearing aids include special tinnitus masking programs designed just for this. JC Audiology offers a wide selection of hearing aids in Lutz, FL.","marks":[]}]}]','f34f0d6',2,'28bb5de');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-03','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Stress Management & Counseling','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01','Stress Management & Counseling','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-68ctwag9","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ywii0ght","text":"Tinnitus and stress often feed off each other. That’s why we recommend activities that calm your mind, like deep breathing, yoga, or light exercise. ","marks":[]}]}]','c999a82',3,'071f662');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-04','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01-04','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Lifestyle Changes','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-01','Lifestyle Changes','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-10y5j8jo","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-jlnqk1bn","text":"Small changes can add up and give you tinnitus relief!","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-kmr57fm3","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3bouh4yz","text":"Cutting back on caffeine and alcohol, protecting your ears in noisy places, staying away from and getting good sleep all support tinnitus relief. Mindfulness and relaxation practices also help lower tinnitus’ volume, so you feel more in control every day.","marks":[]}]}]','c98bee4',4,'61c47db');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-01','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Will tinnitus go away on its own?','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02','Will tinnitus go away on its own?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-yl642uu6","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-r4blw4p3","text":"Sometimes, yes! If caused by a temporary issue like loud noise exposure or earwax buildup, it might fade with time. If it lasts more than a few weeks, it’s time to get checked by a professional.","marks":[]}]}]','178ac08',1,'683a1bb');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-02','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can stress make tinnitus worse?','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02','Can stress make tinnitus worse?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-kpgby0vt","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-4a8twcki","text":"Definitely. Stress and anxiety can make tinnitus feel louder and more annoying. Managing stress often helps reduce how much you notice it.","marks":[]}]}]','3e9e788',2,'d049bb0');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-03','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Is tinnitus always caused by hearing loss?','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02','Is tinnitus always caused by hearing loss?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-t99aq0oh","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-z936ct1r","text":"Not always. While tinnitus often comes with hearing loss, you can have tinnitus and normal hearing too. A hearing test will help figure out what’s going on.","marks":[]}]}]','b48418b',3,'c7a1314');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-04','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-04','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Do hearing aids help with tinnitus?','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02','Do hearing aids help with tinnitus?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2jer7k0q","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7jhp9rpt","text":"Yes! Hearing aids can improve how well you hear real sounds and help mask the ringing inside your ears. Many come with special features made just for tinnitus relief.","marks":[]}]}]','045aeee',4,'9f50a8b');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-05','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02-05','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can ear wax be the reason for my tinnitus?','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support','audiology-services__tinnitus-evaluation-support-accordion-02','Can ear wax be the reason for my tinnitus?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9z303zkl","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-buks13lf","text":"It ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qy2ysin8","text":"could","marks":["em"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-v3z9y6b7","text":" be. Too much earwax can block sounds and cause ringing. If wax is the culprit, safely removing it can often clear up your tinnitus quickly. It would be best to see an audiologist if you are experiencing tinnitus so you can get an accurate diagnosis and the exact triggers can be identified and addressed.","marks":[]}]}]','6c0f0be',5,'3150558');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-01-01','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Ready-Made Hearing Protection','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-01','Ready-Made Hearing Protection','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-rudk5sgf","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-vz8l5goz","text":"These affordable, pre-formed options are quick to use and great for many everyday situations.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-jl3dtsb9","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-l4ja8isg","text":"Earplugs: Inserted into the ear canal to reduce noise in loud places like concerts or busy events.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-otsj4c72","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1htu3nte","text":"Semi-Insert Earplugs: Connected by a flexible band and rest at the ear canal entrance for easy removal.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-se793als","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1q3nx2bs","text":"Earmuffs: Cover the whole ear to block sound from the outside.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-7fxz5qm0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f4w0kwwj","text":"Note: Ready-made options are convenient, but may not fit as securely or comfortably as custom-made products.","marks":["em"]}]}]','34447bc',1,'98418fd');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-01-02','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Custom Hearing Protection','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-01','Custom Hearing Protection','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-lzevo70k","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-m0mecndp","text":"Custom protection is molded to the exact shape of your ear, giving you a personalized fit, long-lasting comfort, and top-level noise reduction.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-m034utu6","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-77p1uf8e","text":"Custom Earplugs: Great for workers, musicians, and anyone regularly around loud sounds.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-vpeqqd7g","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-zvx7paft","text":"Impulse Filter Earplugs: Perfect for hunting and shooting-block dangerous gunshot noise while letting you hear softer sounds like voices or movement.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3emnvbhy","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-vpg1vsqy","text":"Sleep Plugs: Soft and flexible earplugs that help reduce snoring and nighttime noise so you can sleep better.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-mca5ffjq","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-evrm9bq7","text":"In-Ear Monitors (IEMs): High-quality sound devices for musicians and performers that allow clear listening without damaging volume levels.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-yh315ou0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-awxbankg","text":"Digital Hearing Protection (SoundGear): Advanced devices for shooters, hunters, and industrial workers that respond instantly to sudden loud sounds.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1}]','d7b788f',2,'72505c7');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-02-01','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How Custom Ear Molds Are Made','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-02','How Custom Ear Molds Are Made','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1t3v19xd","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-yijc9p7z","text":"Getting custom hearing protection is quick and painless:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-fpjccv81","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3kg9c4yr","text":"Our audiologist or hearing aid specialist takes an impression of your ear using soft material.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"number","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0yefli3s","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-weyuawgz","text":"The mold is sent to a specialized lab.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"number","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-fk2lh2xi","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ervws3v9","text":"Your product is made in your chosen material for a perfect fit.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"number","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9s28ylt8","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-a3sh34w7","text":"The result is comfortable, effective protection that you can wear for hours without discomfort.","marks":[]}]}]','0270634',1,'4a0ef1e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-02-02','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How Long Do Custom Earplugs Last?','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-02','How Long Do Custom Earplugs Last?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hkm0xe0m","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-51k6th64","text":"With good care, custom earplugs can last 3 to 5 years. Their life span depends on how often you use them, how you clean them, and whether your ears change shape over time. We recommend occasional fit checks to make sure they still work properly.","marks":[]}]}]','53763e3',2,'26be887');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03-01','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How do I clean my custom earplugs or molds?','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03','How do I clean my custom earplugs or molds?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-deefeb6m","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-5zgolip4","text":"Wipe them with a soft, dry cloth after each use. For a deeper clean, use mild soap and warm water, then let them dry completely before wearing. Avoid harsh cleaners.","marks":[]}]}]','726bac7',1,'48490b8');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03-02','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I wear custom plugs with other safety gear like helmets?','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03','Can I wear custom plugs with other safety gear like helmets?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-oo382zwl","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-90ncznvh","text":"Yes. Custom plugs fit entirely in the ear, so they work well under helmets and other headgear.","marks":[]}]}]','6d0aaca',2,'b262c12');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03-03','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Will custom earplugs completely block all sound?','custom-hearing-protection','custom-hearing-protection-accordion-03','Will custom earplugs completely block all sound?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-4f487vzt","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-h0a0pbad","text":"No. They are designed to reduce harmful noise while letting you hear safe, important sounds like speech or alarms.","marks":[]}]}]','a1a17ef',3,'92bd570');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-01','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Oticon Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','Oticon Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-uxz9jk13","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-fecno4u5","text":"Oticon has been creating hearing solutions for more than 100 years. Their BrainHearing™ technology helps your brain process sound more easily, so you feel less tired and hear more clearly, even in noisy places. Models like Oticon Intent and Oticon Real offer Bluetooth, tinnitus relief, and a natural, comfortable listening experience. Oticon Intent 2, released in late 2024, builds on their Intent line with even better sound clarity and personalized listening.","marks":[]}]}]','ec5b37b',1,'9ddd543');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-02','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Widex Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','Widex Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-80boruw2","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-hxkmtafb","text":"Widex is known for clear, natural sound. Their hearing aids process sound quickly with almost no delay. Popular models like Widex Moment and Widex SmartRIC help with tinnitus through Zen Therapy and work easily with smartphones for custom adjustments. Widex Allure, launched in early 2025, brings a new chip and the world’s first cloud-based fitting software (Compass Cloud) for a more natural hearing experience.","marks":[]}]}]','bba3239',2,'23fa3c0');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-03','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Phonak Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','Phonak Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-o0c7mlhy","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f8e81dqw","text":"Phonak is a worldwide leader in hearing technology. Models like Phonak Lumity make speech clearer, while Phonak Naída provides strong amplification for people with severe hearing loss. The Phonak Audéo Sphere Infinio uses a deep neural network chip for excellent speech clarity, even in noisy places. Many Phonak aids are rechargeable, stream through Bluetooth, and resist water for daily convenience. Looking for the latest Phonak device? The Infinio platform was expanded in January 2025 with new custom in-the-ear models: Virto Titanium Infinio and Virto 10 NW O Infinio.","marks":[]}]}]','c0c45ab',3,'babec8b');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-04','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-04','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Starkey Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','Starkey Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-g4p4nhs2","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-zqq0a6uy","text":"Starkey hearing aids combine great sound with wellness features such as fall alerts, activity tracking, and tinnitus relief. Models like Starkey Genesis AI and Evolv AI allow hands-free calling, app control, and come with rechargeable options—perfect for active lifestyles. The Edge AI line brings AI sound processing with an ultra-fast neuroprocessor chip and easier wireless streaming via LE Audio.","marks":[]}]}]','0bb6d70',4,'a7f7fb9');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-05','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-05','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'ReSound Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','ReSound Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-qeh0om2a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1e87bnm0","text":"ReSound devices provide natural sound and strong wireless performance. Models like ReSound Vivia and ReSound ONE have personal sound settings, help you hear better in noisy places, and include tinnitus management. Many are rechargeable and work with iOS and Android for streaming. ReSound Vivia, launched in early February 2025, uses Deep Neural Network (DNN) artificial intelligence to improve hearing in noisy places. The ReSound Enzo IA, the world’s smallest rechargeable Super Power hearing aid, ideal for severe to profound loss.","marks":[]}]}]','f0e7482',5,'58a453c');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-06','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-06','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Unitron Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','Unitron Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-w7cjwj7f","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-4gjr7q25","text":"Unitron focuses on comfort and easy use. Their technology changes with your surroundings for smoother listening. The Unitron Blu line includes Bluetooth streaming, app adjustments, and rechargeable batteries. The Smile platform is the newest batch for Unitron. It uses AI-powered sound tuning, improved Bluetooth, and a comfy design for an easy hearing experience.","marks":[]}]}]','dbd39ef',6,'f61b25c');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-07','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01-07','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Signia Hearing Aids','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-01','Signia Hearing Aids','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-39d4sv6o","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-sbzozocy","text":"Signia blends sleek design with strong performance. Models like Pure Charge&Go and Silk X offer clear speech in noise, Bluetooth connection, and discreet styles. Some have Own Voice Processing (OVP) so your voice sounds more natural to you. The Integrated Xperience (IX) platform includes popular models like Styletto AX, Pure Charge&Go AX, and Motion Charge&Go X.","marks":[]}]}]','e8b4f5f',7,'27fd086');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-02-01','hearing-aids-products-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Which hearing aids are the most advanced?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-02','Which hearing aids are the most advanced?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-wpwj0i9o","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-x1yq8g3f","text":"The best hearing aid for you depends on your hearing needs and lifestyle. Many top models have speech clarity features, rechargeability, Bluetooth, and noise reduction.","marks":[]}]}]','7cdeae9',1,'b544a3e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-02-02','hearing-aids-products-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.350Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Which brands help with tinnitus?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-02','Which brands help with tinnitus?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-5kl6w5j2","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-mjpi0wph","text":"Oticon, Widex, and Starkey have special sound therapy programs to ease ringing in the ears.","marks":[]}]}]','8d876e8',2,'b083f51');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-02-03','hearing-aids-products-accordion-02-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'What hearing aids work best for severe hearing loss?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-02','What hearing aids work best for severe hearing loss?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2k3v9dmm","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-617tg4al","text":"Powerful models from Oticon, Phonak, and Starkey are great for people with severe hearing loss.","marks":[]}]}]','b39a248',3,'3343e4a');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-03-01','hearing-aids-products-accordion-03-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Is it safe to sleep with earplugs?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-03','Is it safe to sleep with earplugs?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-j0hc4u72","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-acxpjdvh","text":"Yes, it is safe. Just make sure they are clean and fit well.","marks":[]}]}]','c966b72',1,'4ffad2e');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-03-02','hearing-aids-products-accordion-03-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How long do custom ear molds last?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-03','How long do custom ear molds last?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-ucpgqkbt","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-63u54e6b","text":"Usually 2–5 years, depending on care and changes in your ears.","marks":[]}]}]','3747136',2,'e98b812');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-03-03','hearing-aids-products-accordion-03-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How do I clean my custom earplugs or ear molds?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-03','How do I clean my custom earplugs or ear molds?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-ky7wv2rc","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qmdvy8rt","text":"Wipe them daily with a soft, dry cloth. For a deeper clean, use mild soap and warm water, making sure they are completely dry before using them again. Avoid harsh chemicals, as they can damage the material.","marks":[]}]}]','795bc34',3,'9b87f61');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-04-01','hearing-aids-products-accordion-04-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'What is the most common type of ALD?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-04','What is the most common type of ALD?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3zoz0xi2","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-lrokatrg","text":"TV streamers and personal amplifiers are very popular because they make voices and sound clearer at home, especially when there’s background noise.","marks":[]}]}]','105b096',1,'222ea19');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-04-02','hearing-aids-products-accordion-04-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I use my smartphone as an ALD?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-04','Can I use my smartphone as an ALD?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-s3easj7h","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-va5flgog","text":"Yes. Some hearing aids work with smartphone features like Apple’s Live Listen, which turns your phone into a microphone and sends sound directly to your hearing aids.","marks":[]}]}]','0192606',2,'6472fc8');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products-accordion-04-03','hearing-aids-products-accordion-04-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Do ALDs work without hearing aids?','hearing-aids-products','hearing-aids-products-accordion-04','Do ALDs work without hearing aids?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-y57pcq4p","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-txqfijko","text":"Yes. While many ALDs connect to hearing aids, some (like personal amplifiers) can be used with regular headphones or earbuds.","marks":[]}]}]','0c4c0cd',3,'abae9b8');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-01','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Hearing Loop (Induction) Systems','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01','Hearing Loop (Induction) Systems','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-gdkz6nep","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-d4oz4z9c","text":"Hearing loop systems send sound through electromagnetic signals directly to hearing aids or cochlear implants equipped with telecoils (T-coils). They work well in public venues like churches, theaters, and auditoriums, providing clear sound without extra background noise and allowing for hands-free listening.","marks":[]}]}]','2304ef8',1,'ffdebe6');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-02','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Infrared Systems','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01','Infrared Systems','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-zouj03q6","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-1rk8xutt","text":"Infrared systems use invisible light waves to send sound to a personal receiver. They are usually paired with headphones or a neck loop. Infrared systems are great for private settings such as home TV listening or courtrooms, where privacy is important and radio interference is not an issue.","marks":[]}]}]','2b37d46',2,'c129f82');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-03','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'FM Systems','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01','FM Systems','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-0yvezomd","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-xk42cvte","text":"FM systems send sound via radio waves from a microphone worn by a speaker to a receiver used by the listener. They are popular in classrooms, meetings, and group activities, as they make speech clearer and easier to follow over distance.","marks":[]}]}]','aa969e8',3,'0847a8c');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-04','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-04','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Personal Amplifiers','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01','Personal Amplifiers','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-3qvqr07e","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-xjewbdzi","text":"Small and portable, personal amplifiers use a microphone and headset to boost nearby sounds. They are ideal for one-on-one conversations, quiet group settings, or watching television at home without increasing the volume for everyone else.","marks":[]}]}]','ff7a1f0',4,'bc66b90');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-05','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-05','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'TV Listening Systems','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01','TV Listening Systems','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9et4el9c","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-kphf6buj","text":"These devices stream audio from your TV straight to your hearing aids or wireless headphones. Whether they use Bluetooth, infrared, or radio frequency, they provide clear sound without needing to raise the TV volume.","marks":[]}]}]','c93a957',5,'ce21719');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-06','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01-06','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Alerting Devices','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-01','Alerting Devices','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hy0avdgs","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-twopmknq","text":"As their name implies, alerting devices help individuals stay or be aware of important sounds. They may use flashing lights, vibrations, or loud tones to signal events or important alarms. Alerting devices can be connected with smartphones or smart home systems.","marks":[]}]}]','0ea3172',6,'c217ddb');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-02-01','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'What is the most commonly used ALD?','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-02','What is the most commonly used ALD?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-74lz4wpn","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-dgdf09zb","text":"FM systems are among the most popular, especially in classrooms or group environments, because they deliver the speaker’s voice directly to the listener.","marks":[]}]}]','776a4e9',1,'0e16181');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-02-02','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can ALDs replace hearing aids?','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-02','Can ALDs replace hearing aids?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-g5h3zikm","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-dyb910f9","text":"ALDs can help people with mild hearing loss, but they are not a replacement for hearing aids if you have moderate to severe hearing loss. Most people benefit from using ALDs alongside their hearing aids.","marks":[]}]}]','800305f',2,'68d983c');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-03-01','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-03-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Are ALDs easy to set up?','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-03','Are ALDs easy to set up?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-b6dekp4q","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-aufuaocn","text":"Yes. Most ALDs are user-friendly and come with simple instructions. At JC Audiology, we can set them up for you and show you exactly how to use them.","marks":[]}]}]','6725712',1,'3ada76b');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-03-02','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-03-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Can I take my ALD anywhere?','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-alternatives-accordion-03','Can I take my ALD anywhere?','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-sz07fueo","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qys1ka4o","text":"Many ALDs are portable and can be used in multiple settings, but some (like hearing loops) are installed in specific locations. We can help you choose the right type for your needs.","marks":[]}]}]','a4d685f',2,'cf63b8a');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01-01','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Disposable Zinc-Air Batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01','Disposable Zinc-Air Batteries','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-5qgh87mz","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-5rxmd19f","text":"These are commonly referred to as “button” batteries. They are known to have a long shelf life.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-tiumhr7c","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-i8ouei7h","text":"Disposable batteries can work for many days before needing to be replaced.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-yxjcf7vt","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2c9su0ms","text":"They are color-coded based on their sizes.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-uimg7451","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-o5hsezyn","text":"Size 10 (Yellow)","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-faj0lc4y","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-x7xhul6m","text":"Size 312 (Brown)","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-bob7po90","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-lak9bpid","text":"Size 13 (Orange)","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-cb435xpi","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-939o2xn4","text":"Size 675 (Blue)","marks":["strong"]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1}]','582024a',1,'dbed796');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01-02','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Rechargeable Lithium-Ion Batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01','Rechargeable Lithium-Ion Batteries','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9w1svp2w","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-81s70qdu","text":"These are built into many new hearing aids. They can provide all-day power (around 18-30 hours) and are recommended for individuals with dexterity (vision or hand) issues.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-tnx8xtv7","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-7bj6h012","text":"Rechargeable hearing aid batteries are also preferred by eco-conscious people since they can just be recharged every now and then.","marks":[]}]}]','b1e1e66',2,'2981b08');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01-03','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01-03','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Silver-Zinc Rechargeable Batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-01','Silver-Zinc Rechargeable Batteries','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-e7suited","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qnfjask5","text":"Less common, but some hearing aids still use them. They can be taken out and replaced when needed. Most companies now use lithium-ion instead.","marks":[]}]}]','58aab2e',3,'5bf843d');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-02-01','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-02-01','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'Tips for Making Batteries Last Longer','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-02','Tips for Making Batteries Last Longer','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-lsbqhmsy","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-v04h7ih7","text":"For Disposable Batteries:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-79x97asi","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-45zsx7lp","text":"Wait 5 minutes after removing the tab before use","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-rni0nuuc","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-h2lbmvg3","text":"Store in a cool, dry place (not in the fridge)","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-u1zh14f9","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-dcl2v2gr","text":"Open the battery door at night","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-rsutuqe0","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-az7mg2ib","text":"Keep batteries clean and dry","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9euks4ac","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-wic9ekqe","text":"Carry extras in their case, not loose in your pocket","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hi675iy3","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-6camkscr","text":"For Rechargeable Batteries:","marks":["strong"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-f0lvgyhp","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-5vxla6p6","text":"Charge every night","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-hustfgub","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-732wcht4","text":"Use the charger made for your aids","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1u9zy9ru","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-6qxkkugk","text":"Keep charger and aids dry","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-djns07zy","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-j64g3u37","text":"Turn off if you’re not using them for a while","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1}]','07cc213',1,'be1180c');
INSERT INTO "ec_service_accordion_items" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","service_slug","group_key","question","answer_content","source_element_id","sort_order","answer_widget_id") VALUES('hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-02-02','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-02-02','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z','2026-05-20T20:45:00.351Z',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,'en',NULL,'How to Know When to Change Your Battery','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries','hearing-aids-products__hearing-aid-batteries-accordion-02','How to Know When to Change Your Battery','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b-f4k1zpnx","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-csh2mm0f","text":"Your hearing aid may beep, flash a light, or give a spoken warning when the battery is low.","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-t3uznct1","text":"You might also notice that the sounds coming from the hearing aids are weaker or unclear.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-mnluu9ok","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-y9q3fsd3","text":"If your hearing aids suddenly lose power or the volume becomes intermittent, it might be time for you to open a fresh battery pack.","marks":[]}]}]','a957942',2,'3cd8bc5');
