, is dedicated to making sure you choose the right hearing solution so that you ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-l8y6chk5","text":"hear for life!","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-2159cjr8","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-l8vg6of1","text":"Whether it’s your first time to use hearing aids or looking to improve your current experience, we’ll guide you through every step of the process.","marks":[]}]}]','','0edf44c',1);
