y to handle, fitting inside the outer ear.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-zgv9r315","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-qbm59ocx","text":"Behind-the-Ear (BTE)","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-tehgyo0n","text":": Powerful, flexible, and great for most types of hearing loss.","marks":[]}]}]','','84599ac',9);
