tion as “","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-35c8cdd5","text":"Device Information","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-45f25963","text":".”","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-e0c729f1","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-04bd1101","text":"We collect Device Information using the following technologies:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-06931f1a","style":"normal","markDefs":[{"_key":"link-890b4403","_type":"link","href":"http://www.allaboutcookies.org"}],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-f02c9006","text":"“","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-9b34ed4d","text":"Cookies","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-79cc0b8d","text":"” are data files that are placed on your device or computer and often include an anonymous unique identifier. For more information about cookies, and how to disable cookies, visit ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3195ceed","text":"http://www.allaboutcookies.org","marks":["link-890b4403"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-6588fc0a","text":".","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-5e16101e","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-cf7baa2e","text":"“","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-dcaae61c","text":"Log files","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-0d92c774","text":"” track actions occurring on the Site, and collect data including your IP address, browser type, Internet service provider, referring/exit pages, and date/time stamps. ","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-80d212f4","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3cea77de","text":"“","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-ae9bff14","text":"Web beacons","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-69d3deeb","text":"”, “","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-905a71e1","text":"tags","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-2e5000d1","text":"”, and “","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-312834c7","text":"pixels","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-c24a9fbe","text":"” are electronic files used to record information about how you browse the Site.","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-9c895e53","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-16303916","text":"Additionally, when you make a purchase or attempt to make a purchase through the Site, we collect certain information from you, including your name, billing address, shipping address, payment information (including credit card numbers), email address, and phone number.  We refer to this information as “","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3bd3ef5c","text":"Order Information.","marks":["strong"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-e4d2f8bc","text":"”","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-995c385b","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-77e4dbf6","text":"When we talk about “Personal Information” in this Privacy Policy, we are talking about both Device Information and Order Information.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-dd2d34d2","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-783d87d9","text":"HOW DO WE USE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-5b0bff20","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-310c64c0","text":"We use the Order Information that we collect generally to fulfill any orders placed through the Site (including processing your payment information, arranging for shipping, and providing you with invoices and/or order confirmations).  Additionally, we use this Order Information to:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-fb4cef60","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-fe0e6593","text":"communicate with you;","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-f44536c7","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8bf3e68c","text":"screen our orders for potential risk or fraud; and","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-d67f0465","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-a6df8fde","text":"provide you with information or advertising relating to our products or services (depending on the preferences you have shared with us)","marks":[]}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-65c35b8a","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-466c4eeb","text":"We use the Device Information that we collect to help us screen for potential risk and fraud (in particular, your IP address), and more generally to improve and optimize our Site (for example, by generating analytics about how our customers browse and interact with the Site), and to assess the success of our marketing and advertising campaigns.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1c68c610","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-d3c1d343","text":"SHARING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-b583d5c7","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-758d2861","text":"We may share your Personal Information with third parties as needed to help us use your Personal Information, as described above.  ","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-43376074","style":"normal","markDefs":[{"_key":"link-9b0a8a6b","_type":"link","href":"https://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/"},{"_key":"link-186d7eea","_type":"link","href":"https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout"}],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-6175fd3f","text":"We also use Google Analytics to help us understand how our customers use the Site–you can read more about how Google uses your Personal Information here:  ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-e23d55cd","text":"https://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/","marks":["link-9b0a8a6b"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-cfeb3de1","text":".  You can also opt out of Google Analytics here:  ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-d85ba1f2","text":"https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout","marks":["link-186d7eea"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3ef7d79e","text":".","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-083c9207","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-3548cd93","text":"Finally, we may also share your Personal Information to comply with applicable laws and regulations, to respond to a subpoena, search warrant, or other lawful request for information we receive, or to otherwise protect our rights.","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-1c3d6e5d","style":"h3","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-fadd92d0","text":"BEHAVIOURAL ADVERTISING","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-80320f0a","style":"normal","markDefs":[{"_key":"link-67b2bf0d","_type":"link","href":"http://www.networkadvertising.org/understanding-online-advertising/how-does-it-work"}],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-30af26f9","text":"As described above, we may use your Personal Information to provide you with targeted advertisements or marketing communications we believe may be of interest to you.  For more information about how targeted advertising works, you can visit the Network Advertising Initiative’s (“NAI”) educational page at ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-8768cb21","text":"http://www.networkadvertising.org/understanding-online-advertising/how-does-it-work","marks":["link-67b2bf0d"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s-0d128ea4","text":".","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-fc2494d5","style":"normal","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-be6a48c5","text":"You can opt out of and/or adjust targeted advertising on:","marks":[]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b-bbf2219e","style":"normal","markDefs":[{"_key":"link-30d1f4ea","_type":"link","href":"https://www.facebook.com/settings/?tab=ads"}],"children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s-5e04e139","text":"Facebook by going to ","marks":[]},{"_type":"span","_key":"